channel.title: [508]Fearny Pks 508 Client v2- Sprites, Models
channel.description:
Well my old client had a few issues so i decided to add sprites and models and release.
[b]Features[/b] Sprites Models [IMG]http://i213.photobucket.com/albums/cc28/beast43/model.jpg[/img] Connects to a specific ip Old error fixed(Would not connect correctly)
[size=40pt]Will be updating this repeatedly[/size]
Models
Death cape Dragon Claws A few extra godswords.
Unfortunately one pics but hopefully I am trusted here. You can import models, sprites etc. Any questions ill reply to you via pm or reply.
Click the download pic below(made by me) [URL=http://www.mediafire.com/?vztj2ktoyzy][IMG]http://i213.photobucket.com/albums/cc28/beast43/lunapic-124292422252912.gif[/img][/URL]
Or just click this- http://www.mediafire.com/?vztj2ktoyzy
Thank you.
How to make it connect to your ip.
Open client.java and search [code]beast43.no-ip.biz[/code]
Then change it to your ip. Save and compile.
To make the client say your name at the top. Open applet_sub_1 and search: [code]Fearny[/code] When you see fearny pks v2 508 change it to your name Now save and compile.
Run and it should work. If you dont have a source go here - http://moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,350898.0.html Thanks. :rolleyes:
